Text.string: Oh crap!
Get up!
You got DOWNED, hahaha! Wait, that's not funny.
Bro! Bro! I'm not comin', bro!
Vaughn to the rescue!
No! Bro! No!
Bro-tastrophy! Hold on!
Those bastards!
Just keep shootin'! I'll patch ya up!
This can't be happening! But it is! Hold on!
Don't fail me now, Redbar X2000s!
Not my skin! NOT MY SKIN!
Why can't my abs be ACTUAL steel?
Oh, HELL nah!
Not hiding, just... just not hiding, okay?
They're SHOOTING! At ME!
I'm the one you DON'T shoot at!
Well, I never! I bid you good day!
Running for cover!
Duckin' down! Just for a sec!
Uh... you comin', Vault Hunter?
Yo, Vault Hunter. What's the hold up?
Hey, we should get going... before the COV come back.
Hey, whatcha doin' there? 'Cause we have to leave!
Onward! ... Is what I'd say if I weren't just standing here waiting for you to do something.
Uh... are we just gonna stand here?
Shouldn't we get out of here?
Yeah, cool, all right. I'll just hang. (singing) Just hanging around. Waitin' for this person to do a thing.
Oh, man. And here I thought we were... y'know, doing stuff.
Great. I need a sec to catch my breath.
Warchief down!
Crap crap crap!
They got me!
Ouch! (beat) All right, I'm gonna lie down.
Bandit down! Bandit down!
Woohoo! I am back!
I live!
Blooooooood feud!
I have returned!
Ah yeah, y'all can't hold me down! Who's with me? Just me? Okay. Self-five!
One sec, bro. I gotcha!
Whoa... that looks bad. No, but like... BAD!
Stay still. You don't have a choice!
Fear not, bro!
Just call me the medicine man! On second thought, don't.
Don't. You. Die. On. Me!
No! You must LIVE!
Hang in there, best bro! I shall heal you!
Stay with me, stay with me!
Oh man, you're gonna die! No, I'm just kiddin', I minored in field medicine. And majored in excellence!
Aw YES! First time that worked in awhile!
Now go avenge thyself! Blood feud!
Now go heal your wounded ego with some good old-fashioned revenge!
Yes! Now smite our enemies!
You look better than ever! And that is saying something.
I did it. I am THE MEDICINE MAN!
I saved you! Man, I'm really earning the title of best bro, ya know?
Now stand. And kill! And learn to love again!
Back from the dead! Let's not make this a thing, 'kay?
BALLER!
(gasping breath) Oh, thanks! I needed that.
Hell YEAH!
(emotionally) You. Are. Lovely! And don't let anybody tell you different!
Wow, thought I was a goner. Not really. I'm pretty, ya know, invincible.
Thanks, you!
Appreciate it, bro. More than you can know, bro.
They spilled my blood. It. Is. TIME FOR A BRO-POCALYPSE!
Whew. Nearly stained my undies! Again.
Nice one!
Me and you, thick as bros. Forever!
Crap-sauce!
Grenade!
Incoming!
Boom! Watch out!
Ahhhh!
Hit the deck! I don't know what that means!
Run, run, RUN!
No, no-no-no-no-no!
Yikes!
Damn you to hell!
